"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-sport-524285-paris-olympics-biles-bows-to-queen-andrade-in-iconic-medal-moment\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"US' Simone Biles (silver), Brazil's Rebeca Andrade (gold) and US' Jordan Chiles (bronze) pose during the podium ceremony for the artistic gymnastics women's floor exercise event at the Bercy Arena in Paris, on August 5, 2024.Photo:AFP / Gabriel Bouys  US superstar Simone Biles said it was \\\"just the right thing to do\\\" after she and team-mate Jordan Chiles bowed down to Olympic gold medallist Rebeca Andrade after the floor final in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 2, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999170643626307, \"rank\": 8.291018057028667e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9564995606496911, \"rank\": 0.04437806045615887, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999170643626307, \"rank\": 8.291018057028667e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 200, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.633918959638941e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999170643626307, \"rank\": 8.291018057028667e-05, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.633918959638941e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles had been hoping to win a fourth gold at these Games but a couple of mistakes meant she had to settle for silver behind the Brazilian.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the 27-year-old, who is the world's most decorated gymnast, was far from disappointed and instead joined Chiles in showing admiration to Andrade in one of the iconic images of these Games.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.879240699649344e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio also made history as the first all-Black podium in men or women's gymnastics at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rebeca's so amazing, she's a queen,\\\" said Biles.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's such an excitement to watch and then all the fans in the crowd were always cheering for her, so it was just the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was an all-black podium so that was super-exciting for us, but then Jordan was like 'should we bow to her?'\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.956303822569654, \"rank\": 0.04113782705440339, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and I was like 'absolutely'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles during her floor routine at the Bercy Arena.Photo:AFP / Kaname Muto  Andrade, who lost out on theall-around title to Bileslast week, appreciated the show of respect, saying: \\\"It was very cute of them.\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are the world's best athletes and what they did means a lot to me.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are always rooting for each other, the final is very difficult for everyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles now has 11 Olympic medals after winning team, all-around and vault golds in Paris to go with her floor silver, while she was fifth in the beam final.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.633918959638941e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This story was first published by theBBC.\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  Simone Biles won the vault final to clinch her third gold at the Paris Olympics, dominating the competition with her signature Biles II vault.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9776908220337523, \"rank\": 0.02281823400970121, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The three-dimensional pedant has 546 diamonds and \\\"embodies her unparalleled status in gymnastics,\\\" according to the LA-jeweller that created it.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles' cheeky Instagram post slapped back at criticisms from the former Olympian.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.956904753505915e-21, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999986475814, \"rank\": 1.352387472115238e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"History's most-decorated gymnast is back at the Olympics, rebuilt and renewed - and RNZ'sDana Johanssenwas among the enraptured crowd.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A radiant Biles made her long-awaited Olympic return, drawing boisterous cheers from a star-studded crowd.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  We haveregular online commentaryof local and international sport.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.9992642776189253, \"rank\": 0.0007353509896141441, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 2564, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}]}"